    <h1>Local town facilities</h1>
    <p>
        When you arrive in a new location, you may be fascinated by all of
        the shops and attractions that it has to offer. Contrariwise, you
        may be disappointed in just how little there is to do. This page
        provides a list of all the possible facilities that are in a
        location and brief descriptions.
    </p>
